# Sign In Page Requirements

- Always capture **User ID** and **Password** fields with client-side form validation.
- Include an active cross-link anchor reading **"New User Sign Here"** to route users to registration.
- Never store session tokens or passwords inside open `localStorage`; manage states safely.
